♪ So let's suit up And save the day ♪
translation.de: Komm, hier zeigt jede was sie kann.

translation.en: ♪ Gowns and crowns are always fun, And when it's time to get things done ♪
translation.de: Kronen, Katzen, Charme-Alarm Kleider aus und Hosen an

translation.en: -♪ Princesses wear pants! ♪ -♪ Yeah! ♪
translation.de: Prinzessinnen packen’s an Yeah! Und los!

translation.en: -♪ Let's go! ♪ -♪ Glide or sail, or hop a plane ♪
translation.de: Prinzessinnen packen’s an Yeah! Und los! Zu Land, zu Wasser, in der Luft Kommen wir geschwind, wenn ihr uns ruft.

translation.en: ♪ We'll change the world The Princess way ♪
translation.de: Zu Land, zu Wasser, in der Luft Kommen wir geschwind, wenn ihr uns ruft.

translation.en: -♪ Princesses wear pants! ♪ -♪ Yeah! ♪
translation.de: Wir haben die Hosen an! Yeah!

translation.en: ♪ With the Fruitdoms in our hands ♪ ♪ These Princesses wear pants! ♪
translation.de: Denn hier zeigt jede was sie kann! Prinzessinnen packen’s an!

translation.en: [all] Princess Power!
Okay, Fussy, your "mani-purry" is done.
Did you say "purr-fect"? Glad we agree.
Penny darling, I was just downstairs checking in on, ah, ah!
Uh, I was gonna clean that up.
Penny, I'm not asking for perfection,
but yes... [chuckles] please do clean that up, and... that.
translation.de: aber ja, bitte räum das auf und… das.

translation.en: Take the mess and make it less. Consider it done.
translation.de: Aus Unordnung wird Ordnung. Schon dabei.

translation.en: Thank you.
And I've got just the thing.
My newest creation is ready!
Behold! The Super-Duper Clutter Picker-Upper!
This solution will make a bubble that can pick up any mess anywhere any time.
translation.de: Diese Luftblase räumt alles auf. Überall, jederzeit.

translation.en: It'll revolutionize cleaning all over the Fruitdom!
It's unstoppable, it's unpoppable!
But not Fussy-proof.
I guess it's back to the drawing board.
[gasps] The Charm Alarm!
Kira needs us!
-[purrs] -Come on, Fussy!
♪ Let's go, let's go Na na na na na na ♪
translation.de: Auf los geht's los! Na na na na na na

translation.en: ♪ When the trouble in our world Feels too big for one alone ♪
translation.de: Wenn der Zirkus dieser Welt Zu viel ist für dich allein

translation.en: -♪ Yeah! ♪ -♪ Na na na na na na ♪ -♪ We jump right into action ♪ -♪ That's right! ♪
translation.de: Na na na na na na Sind wir sofort zur Stelle

translation.en: -♪ To help those in need ♪ -♪ Okay! ♪
translation.de: Und helfen in der Not Ok

translation.en: ♪ Every mistake we make ♪ -♪ Is just a step along the way ♪ -Whoo-hoo!
translation.de: Greif nach den Sternen Du kannst aus Fehlern lernen.

translation.en: ♪ So let's go, go, go, Come on let's take on the day ♪
translation.de: Also los, los, los Komm, stellen wir uns dem Tag

translation.en: -♪ Let's take on the day ♪ -♪ Yeah! ♪ ♪ We'll just try 'til we get it right! ♪
translation.de: Stellen wir uns dem Tag! Yeah! Und scheint dir der Weg auch weit

translation.en: ♪ And never give up the fight! ♪
♪ 'Cause that's the Princess way! ♪
Princesses, I need your help!
Mr. Scrumples ran up the fireplace.
translation.de: Herr Krümel lief den Kamin hoch.

translation.en: He's too scared to come down and too high for me to reach him!
translation.de: Jetzt hat er Angst und es ist zu hoch.

translation.en: A trapped Teenykin?
translation.de: Ein Minikin steckt fest? Was für ein Desaster!

translation.en: That's a huge-ikin disaster! Of course we'll help!
translation.de: Ein Minikin steckt fest? Was für ein Desaster! Klar helfen wir.

translation.en: We Pinkie Tea Promise to help those in need.
[all] With our Princess Power, we'll always succeed!
To the Kiwi Fruitdom!
[Penny] Wow, that's a big fireplace.
We're supposed to find one little hamster inside?
Challenge accepted.
Work with me, pal! I'm trying to get you unstuck!
Ugh, now I'm stuck too! Fireplace: one. Bea: zero.
translation.de: Jetzt stecke ich auch fest. Eins zu null für den Kamin.

translation.en: A little help, Princesses?
Any chance you've got a rope in that kit?
Not yet. But I'll fashion up a be-dazzlous one before I can say...
translation.de: Noch nicht, aber ich sage hilda-tastisch:

translation.en: Ta-da!
Hold on, Bea!
Nice pull, Rita.
[pants] Thanks. My fashions are fantabulous and functional.
translation.de: Danke. Meine Mode ist fantabulös und funktional.

translation.en: I tried, but I think Mr. Scrumples only likes you.
translation.de: Ich glaube, Herr Krümel mag nur dich.

translation.en: Bee stings!
If I were a bird, I'd soar up and carry him out! But I can't.
translation.de: Als Vogel würde ich hochfliegen und ihn holen, aber das kann ich nicht.

translation.en: But my unstoppable, unpoppable bubble can!
Your unpoppable, boppable w-w-what?
I can send a bubble up the chimney
translation.de: Ich schicke eine Seifenblase den Kamin hoch.

translation.en: that'll pick up Mr. Scrumples and float him out the top!
translation.de: Ich schicke eine Seifenblase den Kamin hoch. Sie schweben raus.

translation.en: Then I can catch him when he comes out!
translation.de: Dann schnappe ich ihn mir oben.

translation.en: And I'll bring four extra paws so I can't miss. -Come on, Fussy. -[shrieks]
translation.de: Mit vier Extra-Pfoten klappt es. Komm, Fusselchen.

translation.en: This'll be my strongest bubble yet.
Heads up, Kira! It's comin'!
Let's go to the balcony and see if it works.
translation.de: Vom Balkon sehen wir, ob es klappt.

translation.en: Fussy, do you see Mr. Scrumples? Is he close?
translation.de: Fusselchen, siehst du Herrn Krümel? Ist er schon da?

translation.en: [gasps] Fussy!
Oh. The bubble got you. I'm so glad.
translation.de: Die Blase fing dich! So ein Glück!

translation.en: [gasps] And now it got me!
Princesses, look!
Well, on the plus side, your bubble worked.
Too well!
We gotta stop them before they float away!
Or before Fussy pops that bubble!
To the Pineapple plane!
Everything looks so tiny from up here.
It's kinda soothing, don't you think?
Fussy, no! If you pop this bubble, we all fall.
translation.de: Nein! Wenn die Blase platzt, stürzen wir ab.

translation.en: Make a beeline for that bubble!
Science snag. When we get close, the propeller blows it away!
translation.de: Physik-Problem. Der Propeller pustet sie weg.

translation.en: Oh, ruffles! It's spinning out of control toward the Pineapple Fruitdom!
translation.de: Verflixt! Sie taumelt in Richtung Ananas-Fruchtreich.

translation.en: Don't worry, Fussy. We're safe, I promise.
translation.de: Keine Sorge. Wir sind sicher. Versprochen!

translation.en: This is an epic case of bubble trouble!
And it's not over! Now the bubble's headed right for that pelican!
translation.de: Die Blase fliegt auf den Pelikan zu.

translation.en: Uh-oh. That pelican can burst our bubble with his beak.
translation.de: Der Pelikan kann die Blase platzen lassen.

translation.en: Think, think, think.
If I were a bird, what would shoo me away?
A coyote!
Wait!
You don't want to peck that bubble.
translation.de: Nicht in die Blase picken. Du willst

translation.en: You want to peck a tantalizing tuna fish tea sandwich.
translation.de: Nicht in die Blase picken. Du willst ein leckeres Thunfisch-Sandwich.

translation.en: Phew!
[sighs] That was too, too, too close.
And interesting.
The pelican's added weight made the bubble lower a little.
translation.de: Mit dem Pelikan sank die Blase ab.

translation.en: So if my calculations are correct, if we add more weight to the bubble,
translation.de: Wenn wir also mehr Gewicht hinzufügen,

translation.en: it'll get lower and lower until it lands!
translation.de: wird die Blase schwerer und landet.

translation.en: Science success!
Okay! So how do we put things in the bubble if we can't get close to it?
translation.de: Wie bringen wir etwas in die Blase, wenn wir uns nicht nähern können?

translation.en: Oh, oh, oh! I know! It's all in the wrist. And the kit.
translation.de: Ich weiß! Ich hab's am Handgelenk und im Kit.

translation.en: I can fashion up a be-dazzlous slingshot!
Sweet! But where do we find stuff to sling?
Check around your feet!
[gasps] This thing is loaded with stuff! Here you go, Rita!
translation.de: Da ist alles Mögliche! Hier, Hilda.

translation.en: True story: you gotta keep stuff around
'cause you'll never know when you'll have to Princess on the go.
translation.de: Man weiß nie, wann man es braucht.

translation.en: Okay, for real, those boots look so good on you.
translation.de: Im Ernst. Diese Stiefel stehen dir so gut!

translation.en: It's working! Oh, but I'm out of stuff to sling!
translation.de: Es funktioniert! Da ist nichts mehr.

translation.en: Me too! Everything else is bolted down.
Well, I'm not bolted down.
Penny, fly over the bubble. I'm going in!
translation.de: Anna, flieg über die Blase. Ich gehe rein.

translation.en: What? That sounds like the worst idea since socks with sandals!
translation.de: Was? Das ist so schlecht wie Socken in Sandalen.

translation.en: Are you sure?
You got nothing to show for it if you don’t go for it.
Get ready, Bea!
One, two, three.
Go!
Ugh! Am I late for tea?
-[Fussy meows] -Oops! Sorry, Fussy.
-[meows] -Teenykin-tastic timing!
Especially since we're so low in the sky. I think we might be landing.
translation.de: Jetzt fliegen wir niedrig. Wir landen bald.

translation.en: Please return your seats to their full upright position.
Gutter ball. I didn't get us low enough to land.
translation.de: Scheibenhonig! Wir sind nicht tief genug.

translation.en: But Penny's bedroom is right there!
And if this bubble was a puzzle piece,
translation.de: Wenn diese Blase ein Puzzleteil wäre,

translation.en: it would fit right inside Penny's bedroom window!
translation.de: würde sie in Annas Fenster passen!

translation.en: But we're not floating towards Penny's window.
translation.de: Aber wir schweben nicht darauf zu.

translation.en: We will be! Everybody, run with me!
translation.de: Aber gleich. Lauft alle mit mir!

translation.en: For real? They're exercising now?
translation.de: Im Ernst? Sie denken jetzt an Sport?

translation.en: No. They're controlling the bubble's direction!
translation.de: Sie steuern die Flugrichtung der Blase.

translation.en: It's bubble brilliant!
Brace yourself for impact!
Three, two, one!
[Bea] Ricochet bank shot for the win!
Goal!
Game, set, and match, Bea!
Now, we can burst that bubble and set you free!
translation.de: Nun zerplatzen wir sie und lassen euch frei!

translation.en: Wait! If you touch the bubble, you'll get pulled inside too!
translation.de: Warte! Sonst wirst du auch reingezogen.

translation.en: But nothing's Fussy-proof.
It's your time to shine, Fussy!
Duck!
I think you meant "cat."
Huh. This is new.
I never know what kind of surprise I'll find in here.
At least it keeps things interesting.
Hey, pelican. Boots off the bed.
Need help cleaning up, Penny? I would love some help.
